<p>the now-continuing saga of Joey Fucknuts. may he find what he's looking for.</p>
<p>many thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1525332524" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;">Weryllium</a></span> for letting me use his excellent <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3435">SCP-3435</a> and for looking this over.</p>
<p>and thank you, reader, for flying alongside me. ♥</p>
