</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>the ever-scintillating and brilliant <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hexadon" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2139646); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2139646&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1525332524" alt="HexaDon" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2139646)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hexadon" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2139646); return false;">HexaDon</a></span> has gifted us with a doodle of our fair hero: <a href="https://i.imgur.com/lNzs6Vj.jpg">https://i.imgur.com/lNzs6Vj.jpg</a><br />
gotta admit, never thought of him wearing a beard, but it ain't half bad.</p>

